snippet.title: Best VGM 2056 - Etrian Odyssey IV - Labyrinth V ~ City of Radiant Ruin
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1192 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V39OyFbkevY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 3DS
Etrian Odyssey IV (2012)
Labyrinth V ~ City of Radiant Ruin
Yuzo Koshiro
